/-!
# Pointless Scheme

This is the main import file for the pointless scheme project, which develops
algebraic geometry using locales (pointless topology) instead of point-set topology.

## Structure

The project is organized into the following modules:

1. `FoundationalLocaleTheory` - Basic frame and locale theory
2. `ZariskiLocale` - The Zariski locale as the frame of radical ideals
3. `Functoriality` - Functorial behavior of Spec
4. `StructureSheaf` - The structure sheaf on Zariski locales
5. `LocallyRingedLocale` - Locally ringed locales and schemes
6. `BasicProperties` - Basic properties of schemes
-/
